==選舉結果==
總投票率為57.56%。復興黨贏得了250席位中200席（80%），而反對黨在國內外抵制選舉。兩個{{le|敘利亞的亞美尼亞人|Armenians in Syria|亞美尼亞人}}當選為敘利亞人民議會議員，當中首度有亞美尼亞女性進入議會<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://armenianweekly.com/2016/04/16/two-armenians-elected-to-syrias-parliament/ |title=Two Armenians Elected to Syria’s Parliament |accessdate=2016-04-18 |archive-date=2016-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417194339/http://armenianweekly.com/2016/04/16/two-armenians-elected-to-syrias-parliament/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

